---
const highlights = [
  {
    title: "显示器和桌面",
    titleEn: "Display and desktop",
    body: "亮度、分辨率、夜览、外接屏回退链路和菜单栏空间管理集中处理。",
    bodyEn: "Brightness, resolution, Night Shift, fallback routes, and desktop space controls stay close.",
  },
  {
    title: "清理和维护",
    titleEn: "Cleanup and maintenance",
    body: "磁盘缓存、Xcode 派生数据、废纸篓和损坏应用修复都有明确的安全边界。",
    bodyEn: "Disk caches, Xcode data, Trash, and damaged app fixes run with explicit safety boundaries.",
  },
  {
    title: "启动和自动化",
    titleEn: "Launch and automate",
    body: "启动台、App 快捷键、剪贴板、锁屏和常用系统动作使用全局快捷键触发。",
    bodyEn: "Launch apps, run shortcuts, clear clipboard, lock the screen, and trigger common actions fast.",
  },
  {
    title: "插件化扩展",
    titleEn: "Plugin extension",
    body: "插件包、在线 catalog、权限卡片和设置页由宿主统一管理。",
    bodyEn: "Plugin packages, online catalogs, permissions, shortcuts, and settings share one host system.",
  },
];
---

<section class="showcase" id="features" aria-labelledby="features-title">
  <div class="section-heading">
    <h2 id="features-title">
      <span data-i18n-zh>系统工具，统一入口。</span>
      <span data-i18n-en>System utilities, one entry point.</span>
    </h2>
    <p>
      <span data-i18n-zh>菜单栏快速执行，组件面板持续查看，设置页管理权限、快捷键和插件。</span>
      <span data-i18n-en>Run actions from the menu bar, monitor state in components, and manage permissions, shortcuts, and plugins in settings.</span>
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="feature-strip" aria-label="核心能力">
    {highlights.map((item) => (
      <article>
        <h3>
          <span data-i18n-zh>{item.title}</span>
          <span data-i18n-en>{item.titleEn}</span>
        </h3>
        <p>
          <span data-i18n-zh>{item.body}</span>
          <span data-i18n-en>{item.bodyEn}</span>
        </p>
      </article>
    ))}
  </div>
</section>
